<p><strong>1. What is the author's intent in writing this book?</strong></p>
<p>The primary focus of this book is to provide a comprehensive introduction to quantum mechanics at the undergraduate level. It aims to equip students with a solid understanding of the fundamental concepts, principles, and applications of quantum mechanics.</p>
<p><strong>2. Is this book suitable for students with no prior knowledge of quantum mechanics?</strong></p>
<p>Yes, this book is designed to cater to students with little or no background in quantum mechanics. It assumes no prior knowledge of the subject and gradually builds up from the basics to more advanced concepts.</p>
